    <h1 class="display-lg post-title">First Time Home Buyer Programs: Escape The Renter Trap</h1>
    <div class="post-byline"><span class="mono">By Jim Blackburn · NMLS #1072866</span><span class="post-byline__sep">·</span><time datetime="2025-07-04">2025-07-04</time></div>
  </header>

  <figure class="container-prose post-hero">
    <img src="/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/ChatGPT-Image-Nov-5-2025-11_42_32-PM.png" alt="First Time Home Buyer Programs: Escape The Renter Trap" width="1200" height="675" loading="eager" />
